 Pralatrexate, Fludarabine, Decitabine, Azacitidine, Capecitabine', 'Budesonide, Cromoglicic acid, Prednisolone, Betamethasone, Beclomethasone dipropionate', 'Moderate', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/38556/', '[1] "Product Information. Clolar (clofarabine)." sanofi-aventis, Bridgewater, NJ.', 1767369485);
