ic infection, or sepsis develops, baricitinib should be interrupted until the infection is controlled.', 'Others', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Baricitinib, Tofacitinib, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab', 'Apremilast, Pirfenidone, Belumosudil, Teprotumumab, Emapalumab, Ravulizumab, Pegcetacoplan, Eculizumab, Sutimlimab, Efalizumab', 'Major', NULL, 'DDInter', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/38738/', '[1] "Product Information. Olumiant (baricitinib)." Lilly, Eli and Company, Indianapolis, IN.[2] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[3] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0', 1767369485);
